### Update Profile - Minimal Required
PUT https://localhost:7000/api/UserProfile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "university": "University of Jordan",
  "major": "Computer Science",
  "expectedGraduationYear": 2026,
  "currentLevel": 0,
  "timezone": "UTC"
}

### Validate Timezone - Valid
GET https://localhost:7000/api/UserProfile/validate-timezone?timezone=Asia/Amman

### Validate Timezone - Invalid
GET https://localhost:7000/api/UserProfile/validate-timezone?timezone=Invalid/Timezone

### Get Timezones - No Location
GET https://localhost:7000/api/UserProfile/timezones

### Get Timezones - With Location
GET https://localhost:7000/api/UserProfile/timezones?location=Jordan

### Get Profile
GET https://localhost:7000/api/UserProfile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Check Profile Exists
GET https://localhost:7000/api/UserProfile/exists
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Completion
GET https://localhost:7000/api/UserProfile/completion
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
